DISCLAIMER:

This software was co-developed with Claude AI (Anthropic) as a demonstration of thermal fatigue lifetime prediction methodology. It uses publicly available parameters and data to showcase technical approaches while respecting confidentiality requirements of proprietary work.

This tool is for educational and demonstration purposes. For production
applications, users should:
- Use device-specific characterization data
- Validate against physical testing and field data
- Consult with reliability engineers and component suppliers
- Follow appropriate qualification procedures

